  <diagram id="cS_z8Mcy1D7Kebro-Lss" name="Page-2">
    <mxGraphModel dx="1534" dy="862" grid="1" gridSize="10" guides="1" tooltips="1" connect="1" arrows="1" fold="1" page="1" pageScale="1" pageWidth="850" pageHeight="1100" math="0" shadow="0">
      <root>
        <mxCell id="0" />
        <mxCell id="1" parent="0" />
        <UserObject label="" mermaidData="{&#xa;  &quot;data&quot;: &quot;sequenceDiagram\n    autonumber\n    participant Caller as Caller&lt;br/&gt;(orchestrate_codeact.py)\n    participant ACAS as ACAS Sandbox Group&lt;br/&gt;(Microsoft.App/sandboxGroups)\n    participant FHA as FHA microVM&lt;br/&gt;(agent/main.py + ResponsesHostServer)\n    participant Sbx as ACAS Sandbox&lt;br/&gt;(Python 3.13, ephemeral)\n    participant Model as Foundry Model&lt;br/&gt;(gpt-5.4 deployment)\n\n    Caller-&gt;&gt;ACAS: begin_create_sandbox(disk=\&quot;python-3.13\&quot;)\n    ACAS--&gt;&gt;Caller: sandbox_id\n\n    Caller-&gt;&gt;FHA: POST /agents/&lt;name&gt;/.../responses&lt;br/&gt;Authorization: Bearer &lt;token&gt;&lt;br/&gt;x-acas-sandbox-id: &lt;sandbox_id&gt;&lt;br/&gt;body: { input, previous_response_id }\n    Note over FHA: Cold: boot microVM, ~12s&lt;br/&gt;Warm: reuse pinned microVM, ~5s&lt;br/&gt;(pinned by previous_response_id)\n\n    rect rgb(245,245,255)\n    Note over FHA,Model: Agentic loop — repeats until model decides it&#39;s done\n    FHA-&gt;&gt;Model: POST /openai/v1/chat/completions&lt;br/&gt;(via FoundryChatClient, prompt + tool defs)\n    Model--&gt;&gt;FHA: tool_call: execute_code(code=\&quot;...\&quot;)\n    FHA-&gt;&gt;Sbx: exec via acas-toolkit SandboxPool&lt;br/&gt;(bound to x-acas-sandbox-id from ContextVar)\n    Sbx--&gt;&gt;FHA: { stdout, stderr, exit_code, duration_ms }\n    FHA-&gt;&gt;Model: tool_result\n    Model--&gt;&gt;FHA: final assistant text\n    end\n\n    FHA--&gt;&gt;Caller: Responses envelope&lt;br/&gt;{ id, output_text, usage, ... }\n    Caller-&gt;&gt;ACAS: delete_sandbox(sandbox_id)&quot;,&#xa;  &quot;config&quot;: null&#xa;}" id="JOvCdeo2ayduRxTeZ4Yt-1">
